data.description:
Beautiful move in ready two-story boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Step inside to discover elegant tile throughout the entry and high ceilings in the living area, crowned by a marble fireplace mantle. Upgraded hardwood floors grace the master, stairway, and game room upstairs. The generously appointed kitchen, featuring elegant dark cabinets, invites culinary exploration and overlooks both the inviting breakfast nook and the expansive backyard beyond. Tucked away in a quiet cul-de-sac, this home offers serenity and style. Refrigerator, washer, dryer, and TVs included. Schedule your viewing today and submit your application.
